{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6540d1f356","title":"中央转发华北局关于春耕生产的指示的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"defe90c63d","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":4,"articleId":"6540d1f356","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"05ce75119c","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"6540d1f356","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华北局1953年3月2日关于春耕生产给蒙绥分局、各省委转各县委（旗委）并报中央的指示。指示中说，目前农村的中心工作很多，很紧道，领导机关又正集中精力进行反官停主义、反命令主义、反违法乱纪的斗争。如果没有适当安排，春耕生产势必受到严重的影响，因此分局、各省委应明确指示各县（旗）委，在农村中当前压倒一切的中心任务，应当是加紧春耕的准备工作和开始进行春耕生产，为今年农业增产打好基础。其他一切工作都必须围绕并结合春耕生产来进行，凡是影响与阻碍春耕生产这一中心任务的，均应改变、推迟或缩小原来的计划，以切实保证春耕生产的顺利进行。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3f19f13638","type":"title","text":"中央转发华北局关于春耕生产的指示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"6540d1f356","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05ce75119c","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局、分局，并转省市委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"6540d1f356","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"622faf6851","type":"paragraph","text":"在农村目前春耕是压倒一切的工作，其他工作应是配合进行。华北局三月二日的文件是正确的，请你们仿此作出自己的部署","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"6540d1f356","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fe29924fd","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"6540d1f356","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"378abf43b4","type":"paragraph","text":"三月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"6540d1f356","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":535,"end":535}}}},"__N_SSG":true}